  /* Graphics Toolbox

    ┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈
    ──────────────────────
    ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    ▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬
    ▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄
    ██████████████████████

    ══════════════════════
    •••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••
    ◆◇◆◇◆◇◆◇◆◇◆◇◆◇◆◇◆◆◇◆◇◆◇◆◇◆◇◆◇◆◇◆◇


   ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
   │ SECTION NAME                        │
   └──


    Arrows:
      ➔
      ← → ↑ ↓ ↔ ↕ ↖ ↗ ↘ ↙                                       (Simple Arrows)
      ⇐ ⇒ ⇑ ⇓ ⇔ ⇕ ⇖ ⇗ ⇘ ⇙                                    (Double Arrows)
      ↩ ↪ ↵ ↴ ↶ ↷ ↺ ↻                                 (Curved/Circular Arrows)
      ➧ ➨ ➩ ➪ ➫ ➬ ➭ ➮ ➯ ➱                                   (Dingbat Arrows)
      ► ◄ ▲ ▼ ▸ ◂ ▴ ▾                                  (Block/Triangle Arrows)
      ➢➣➤➥⇢⇠➵➸➳➽                                    (Fancy/Pointed Arrows)

      Box Drawing & Borders:
      ─ │ ┌ ┐ └ ┘ ├ ┤ ┬ ┴ ┼                                        (Light)
      ━ ┃ ┏ ┓ ┗ ┛ ┣ ┫ ┳ ┻ ╋                                        (Heavy)
      ═ ║ ╔ ╗ ╚ ╝ ╠ ╣ ╦ ╩ ╬                                       (Double)
      ╌ ╎ ┄ ┆ ┈ ┊ ┉ ┋                                         (Dashed/Dotted)
      ╭ ╮ ╯ ╰ ╱ ╲ ╳                                         (Curved/Diagonal)
      ╴╵╶╷                                                            (Half Lines)

      Block Elements:
      ▀ ▄ █ ▌ ▐ ░ ▒ ▓                                          (Shades/Blocks)
      ■ □ ▪ ▫ ▬                                                 (Geometric Shapes)
      ▢ ▣ ▤ ▥ ▦ ▧ ▨ ▩                                      (Patterned Squares)

      Geometric Shapes:
      ○ ● ◎ ◉ ◇ ◆ ◈                                           (Circles, Diamonds)
      ◊ △ ▲ ▽ ▼ ◁ ◀ ▷ ▶                                            (Triangles)
      ◌         ◦                                                  (Small Circles)

      Stars & Asterisks:
      ★ ☆ ✡ ✶ ✷ ✸ ✹ ✺ ✻ ✼ ✽ ✾                                     (Stars)
      ※ ＊﹡                                             (Asterisks/Sparkles)

      Punctuation & Symbols:
      · • … ⋮ ⋯ ⋰ ⋱                                           (Dots, Ellipses)
      ¡ ¿ § ¶ © ® ™                                           (General Symbols)
      ¦ ¨ ¯ ´ `                                              (Accents as lines)

      Mathematical & Technical:
      × ÷ ± √ ∞ ≠ ≈ ≡ ≤ ≥                                         (Common Math)
      ∧ ∨ ¬ ∈ ∉ ∀ ∃                                               (Logic, Sets)
      ∴ ∵                                                  (Therefore, Because)

      Braille Patterns                               (can be used for textures):
      ⠀ ⠁ ⠂ ⠄ ⡀ ⢀ ⠈ ⠐ ⠠ ⡄ ⠎ ⠕ ⡆ ⡇ ⡗ ⡿
      ⣿ ⠿ ⡻ ⢟ ⢫ ⢯ ⣛ ⣟ ⣯ ⣷ ⣶ ⣼ ⣸ ⢸ ⣰

      Miscellaneous Dingbats:
      ✓ ✔ ✗ ✘                                               (Check/Cross Marks)
      ✿ ❀ ❁ ❂ ❃ ❄ ❅ ❆                                   (Flowers, Snowflakes)
      ❦ ❧                                                       (Floral Hearts)
      ❍ ❏ ❐ ❑ ❒                                           (Geometric Dingbats)
      ♩ ♪ ♫ ♬                                                  (Musical Notes)
      ⚐ ⚑                                                                (Flags)
      ☉ ☼☽☾                                                         (Sun, Moon)

  */

